You've finally solved it. Who knew that leaving dead stars long enough would cause your artificial Solar System to implode on itself and lead to the Big Bang? 

If only you could tap into that much mass right before it started expanding again, then you could literally have the entire Universe in the palm of your hands.

[note]Your third and final material from the EOH.

Use your first few to upgrade your EOH to Tier 9 so you can get more Universium.

Maybe it's time to make multiple Eyes now.

Congrats! You can move to the UXV tier.[/note]
